{"id": "art-25149", "label": "Art. 25149", "title": "Art. 25149", "slug": "art-25149", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_908434216\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1443\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_908434216\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>49</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1148940451\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1442\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1148940451\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Asocia&#355;ii</span> care nu au\nvotat în favoarea transform&#259;rii au dreptul de a se retrage din societate <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de a <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;ine</span>\ncump&#259;rarea <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social de\nc&#259;tre societate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1763110627\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1441\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1763110627\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dreptul de retragere poate fi exercitat în termen de 30\nde zile de la data adopt&#259;rii hot&#259;rârii adun&#259;rii generale a <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>, cu <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ia</span>\nnotific&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>inten&#355;iei</span> de retragere cel mai\ntârziu în cadrul adun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1068399956\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1440\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1068399956\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<span class=SpellE>Asocia&#355;ii</span> depun la sediul\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>declara&#355;ia</span>\nscris&#259; de retragere, în care precizeaz&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ndac&#259; sunt de acord cu <span class=SpellE>pre&#355;ul</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social stabilit în\nproiectul de transformare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> confirmat de\nexpertul independent, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span>\nsociale sau alte titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social pe care le\nposed&#259; sau, dup&#259; caz, certificatele de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span>\nemise potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 97. <span\nclass=SpellE>Declara&#355;ia</span> se poate transmite <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nîn format electronic la adresa de e-mail indicat&#259; în acest scop în\nproiectul de transformare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1058952482\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1439\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1058952482\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<span class=SpellE>Pre&#355;ul</span> pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span>\nsociale sau alte titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social ale\nasociatului care <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> exercit&#259; dreptul de\nretragere, stabilit de societate în proiectul de transformare <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> confirmat în raportul de evaluare al expertului\nindependent, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>45</sup>,\nse <span class=SpellE>pl&#259;te&#351;te</span> în termen de dou&#259; luni de\nla data la care transformarea transfrontalier&#259; produce efecte, potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>55</sup>, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> cazului în care un termen mai scurt este\nprev&#259;zut în proiectul de transformare sau este agreat de <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1008022284\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1438\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1008022284\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Certificatul prealabil transform&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere poate fi emis numai dac&#259; societatea prezint&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> suficiente pentru plata/dovezi privind <span\nclass=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span> disponibilului b&#259;nesc pentru plata, în\ntermenul prev&#259;zut de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i> sau\nconvenit de <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span>, a <span class=SpellE>pre&#355;ului</span>\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1282774664\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1437\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1282774664\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)În termen de 15 zile de la data împlinirii termenului\nprev&#259;zut la alin. (2), asociatul care, <span class=SpellE>exercitându-&#351;i</span>\ndreptul de retragere, <span class=SpellE>sus&#355;ine</span> c&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>pre&#355;ul</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social nu are caracter adecvat poate cere <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> <span class=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span>\nobligarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> la plata unei <span\nclass=SpellE>compensa&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>b&#259;ne&#351;ti</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_732581649\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1436\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_732581649\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Cererea privind stabilirea <span class=SpellE>compensa&#355;iei</span>\n<span class=SpellE>b&#259;ne&#351;ti</span> prev&#259;zute la alin. (6) se\njudec&#259; de <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncu prec&#259;dere, hot&#259;rârea fiind supus&#259; doar apelului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2073252207\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1435\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2073252207\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Societatea pune de îndat&#259;, la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span>\ncreditorilor ale c&#259;ror <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;e</span> sunt\nanterioare datei efectu&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>publicit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nproiectului de transformare, cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> în format\nelectronic, <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind num&#259;rul <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> care au notificat <span class=SpellE>inten&#355;ia</span>\nde a exercita dreptul de retragere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1564928647\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1434\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1564928647\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i>\nromân&#259;, ca <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i> a statului de\nplecare, este <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legea</i> aplicabil&#259;\ndreptului de retragere a asociatului, iar tribunalul în a c&#259;rui <span\nclass=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span> se afl&#259; sediul social al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ce face obiectul transform&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere este <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span> competent&#259;\ns&#259; <span class=SpellE>solu&#355;ioneze</span> cererea pentru stabilirea <span\nclass=SpellE>compensa&#355;iei</span> <span class=SpellE>b&#259;ne&#351;ti</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> orice alt litigiu privind acest drept.</span></p>"}